//! # Incremental Compilation
//!
//! High-performance incremental compilation system:
//!
//! - **Content-Addressable Cache**: Artifacts indexed by cryptographic hash
//! - **Fine-Grained Dependencies**: Function/type level tracking
//! - **Minimal Rebuilds**: Only recompile what's affected by changes
//! - **Parallel Safe**: Lock-free concurrent cache access
//!
//! ## How It Works
//!
//! ```text
//! Source Files → Change Detection → Dependency Analysis → Selective Recompilation
//!      │                │                  │                     │
//!      ▼                ▼                  ▼                     ▼
//!  File Hash        Compare          Build Graph          Compile Only
//!  Fingerprint      Signatures       Traversal            Changed Units
//! ```
//!
//! ## Cache Structure
//!
//! ```text
//! ~/.quanta/cache/
//! ├── artifacts/           # Compiled artifacts by hash
//! │   ├── a1b2c3d4...     # Object files, MIR, metadata
//! │   └── ...
//! ├── deps/                # Dependency graphs
//! │   ├── project.deps    # Project-wide dependencies
//! │   └── ...
//! └── index.db            # Cache index database
//! ```

